snippet.title: (SM64 Mini) Super Slide 64 RELEASE (V1.0.1)
snippet.description:
The full release to Super Slide 64! Race over 20 slides to collect 48 stars! Have fun!

Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hhzAV5AvTIAqATafAt3tLtZmlqKaSDLb/view

Fixes:
(v1.0.1)
-added a few objects
-fixed some broken warps
-fixed broken objects and star IDs (old version gave you a 49th star by mistake)

Music:

Ib - Memory: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=69Dix-v4h-I
Sonic Rush Adventure - Coral Cave Zone: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EIWOGgoFLZo
_________________________________________________________________
All other projects (as zip): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1i4q28hpkfH32--YtsE4JX9otwAoJVm-a/view?usp=sharing

_________________________________________________________________
Patreon: http://patreon.com/sm64pie
Twitter: http://twitter.com/sm64pie
Twitch: http://twitch.tv/sm64pie
Soundcloud: http://soundcloud.com/pieordie1

Other stuff:

Bowser's Dank Rave 8 - https://youtu.be/HlBynqZr6WQ

Star Matrix Preview 2 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iQHYbYI86Ys
